Hinamatsuri Operation: Prepare 5 Hishimochi. Successfully modernize a Ayanami-class DD with 5 Fubuki-class DDs at the same time, twice.
* Ayanami-class DDs are {{ShipLink|Ayanami}}, {{ShipLink|Shikinami}}, {{ShipLink|Amagiri}}, {{ShipLink|Sagiri}}, {{ShipLink|Oboro}}, {{ShipLink|Akebono}}, {{ShipLink|Sazanami}}, {{ShipLink|Ushio}}.
* Fubuki-class DDs are {{ShipLink|Fubuki}}, {{ShipLink|Shirayuki}}, {{ShipLink|Hatsuyuki}}, {{ShipLink|Miyuki}}, {{ShipLink|Murakumo}}, {{ShipLink|Usugumo}}, {{ShipLink|Isonami}}, {{ShipLink|Uranami}}

Bw1.detail_en:
''Sortie for the week with all forces, spot as many enemy fleets as possible, and confront them!''
*Completion Condition: Fulfill all of the following.
*# Sortie 36 times ('''NOT 36 battles''');
*# Reach boss node 24 times;
*# Win at boss node 12 times;
*# Obtain 6 S-rank victories (does not have to be at boss).
*Each category contributes 25% towards the quest progress, so the 50% / 80% display is not a good benchmark for this quest.
